She nodded, more out of habit, "Of course," to his first command. Then, "She 
does her duty without question. She's good thus far. As to appreciate, it is 
too early to tell. If & when she is faced with the face of who she once was & 
decides to stay a Predacon, then that is when I shall appreciate her more so. 
However, she has a devotion well enough to her comrades." she informed him. She 
was rather curious, somewhat, why he asked these questions. But dismissed 
them as his own curiousity to know how Blackstorm was doing in her new mode. 

--part1_107.2365fcf1.2c05bc3d_boundary
